WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:11.440
People with high ideals will never die.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.400
The spirit of the harmonica lasts forever.

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:18.090
What's with the 'Binjiang Times'?

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:20.720
Publishing anti-Manchu remarks

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:23.640
to sabotage the Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:25.560
Especially the article in it,

00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:29.410
which openly complains about Gu Xiaoxiong's death.

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:30.640
It points

00:01:31.240 --> 00:01:33.170
directly at the Police Department

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.000
and at me.

00:01:34.479 --> 00:01:35.479
Who is the author?

00:01:35.479 --> 00:01:37.960
The author of this article is Zhou Zhi.

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:40.640
He is an accomplice of Gu Xiaoxiong.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.360
As the Chief of the Special Branch,

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:43.420
what do you even do?

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:45.320
Why aren't you arresting such an anti-Japanese element?

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:46.120
Keep him alive

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:48.740
so he can use his pen to confuse the public

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:51.210
and go against the Great Japanese Empire?

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:53.810
I just found out about this person.

00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:56.640
I will issue a wanted poster immediately,

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:57.900
post it on the streets,

00:01:58.039 --> 00:01:59.840
and do everything to arrest him.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.920
Suspect Zhou Zhi

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:04.370
publicly made anti-Manchurian remarks,

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:07.000
vainly attempting to destroy the Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere,

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:08.600
shaking public confidence,

00:02:08.680 --> 00:02:10.610
and endangering public security.

00:03:09.320 --> 00:03:10.000
Who are you?

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:10.800
What are you doing?

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:11.840
Where is the guy who just passed by?

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:13.000
Who? I don't know.

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:14.680
Get lost.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:25.760
Mr. Zhou, come with me.

00:03:27.120 --> 00:03:27.560
Where to?

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:28.160
This way.

00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:28.960
Okay.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:35.880
Thank you.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:39.960
Brother Shen.

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:42.520
Mr. Zhou is Xiaoxiong's friend

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:45.200
and a frequent visitor to our harmonica club.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.680
Today, I want to specially thank

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:48.360
Mr. Shen for coming to my rescue.

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:49.960
Mr. Zhou, there's no need for that.

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:52.840
Actually, I am also a regular at the harmonica club.

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:54.120
Please sit.

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:56.079
Brother, this is the author who serializes

00:03:56.079 --> 00:03:57.680
martial arts novels in the Binjiang Times,

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:58.760
Yisuo Yanyu.

00:03:59.600 --> 00:04:00.360
Really?

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:01.600
I'm flattered.

00:04:02.440 --> 00:04:03.240
Mr. Zhou,

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.160
I don't have much education,

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:07.240
but your novel in the literature section on the third page,

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:09.200
I read it every issue.

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:11.560
I can tell

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:13.120
the big villain you mentioned

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:14.850
is an allusion to the Japanese.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:19.240
I've finally met someone who truly understands me today.

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:21.880
I definitely deserve to be called that.

00:04:22.280 --> 00:04:23.520
Every issue of your novel,

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:24.800
I cut out

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:26.120
and bind into a book.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:27.440
When I can't sleep at night,

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:28.680
I'll flip through it.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.120
Mr. Zhou, could you reveal

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:34.080
in the ending,

00:04:34.880 --> 00:04:36.940
how it turns out for that big villain?

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:41.040
Mr. Shen,

00:04:42.600 --> 00:04:43.400
I'm sorry.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:45.360
I'm afraid

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:47.460
you won't be able to see my ending.

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:49.120
Look at me.

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:51.400
I'm stuck at my desk all day,

00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:53.960
writing either novels or editorials.

00:04:54.640 --> 00:04:57.320
But nothing can stop the iron hooves of the Japanese.

00:04:57.320 --> 00:04:58.240
Besides,

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:00.020
I can no longer stay in Harbin.

00:05:01.120 --> 00:05:02.200
I've made up my mind

00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:05.320
to go to the rear area.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:10.760
Mr. Zhou.

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:13.360
How do you plan to leave Harbin?

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.920
That's exactly what I'm worrying about.

00:05:17.920 --> 00:05:20.240
I was going to discuss it with Miss Qin,

00:05:20.760 --> 00:05:21.600
but when I got to the street,

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:23.120
I was tailed by spies.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:24.880
Shen.

00:05:25.320 --> 00:05:26.480
I was thinking of

00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:27.640
having Mr. Zhou leave

00:05:27.640 --> 00:05:29.770
with the kids from the harmonica club.

00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:32.210
Chen Yu is about to become our comrade.

00:05:32.320 --> 00:05:33.560
He will help too.

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:35.159
No problem.

00:05:35.640 --> 00:05:36.370
Don't worry.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:37.720
I will do my best

00:05:37.880 --> 00:05:39.760
to help you leave Harbin safely.

00:05:40.640 --> 00:05:41.320
Thank you.

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:42.640
Don't thank me yet.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:45.159
If I send you to the rear,

00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:46.680
you must promise me one thing.

00:05:46.680 --> 00:05:47.440
Go ahead.

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:50.200
Hurry up and write the ending for me.

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:51.580
I'm waiting to read it.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:52.800
Okay.

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:54.600
I promise you.

00:05:54.760 --> 00:05:55.960
Good. It's settled.

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:06.280
Don't worry, Mr. Zhou.

00:06:06.280 --> 00:06:07.280
It's safe now.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:08.680
Thank you.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:11.800
Miss Qin.

00:06:12.240 --> 00:06:12.960
Goodbye.

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.800
Mr. Zhou, have a safe trip.

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:15.880
Rest assured.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:16.930
When I get there,

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:18.240
I will tell everyone

00:06:18.440 --> 00:06:21.040
that the harmonica in Harbin is still playing.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:24.970
Goodbye, Boss Shen.

00:06:25.480 --> 00:06:26.480
We'll meet again.

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:29.360
Words cannot express my gratitude.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:30.400
Goodbye.

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:31.840
Goodbye.

00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:34.680
Goodbye.

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:36.760
Goodbye.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:38.880
Goodbye, Xiao Lin and Xiao Zhou.

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:40.140
Take care of everyone.

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:50.120
You don't need to worry.

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.600
With Zhan Li and A Jin on the way,

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:53.060
the children will be fine.

00:06:53.320 --> 00:06:55.240
Once across the river and in Acheng,

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:57.900
that's the jurisdiction of the Third Squadron.

00:06:58.159 --> 00:06:58.960
Captain Liu

00:06:59.200 --> 00:07:01.330
is a good friend of mine for many years.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.800
As long as the comrades at the liaison point

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:05.460
send Mr. Zhou and the children

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.120
to the Great Rear Area in the southwest,

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:09.120
they will be safe.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:12.120
They are safe now.

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:13.440
Have you thought about yourself?

00:07:13.440 --> 00:07:14.760
If Matsuda finds out

00:07:14.960 --> 00:07:16.690
you transferred the children,

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.680
you will be in big trouble.

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:20.640
Yes, brother.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:22.880
I advised Sister Qin several times

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:24.240
to go with the children,

00:07:24.520 --> 00:07:25.920
but she wouldn't listen.

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:28.450
I'll tell you the truth.

00:07:29.040 --> 00:07:30.600
The reason it went so smoothly this time

00:07:30.600 --> 00:07:31.680
is because Chen Yu

00:07:31.880 --> 00:07:34.600
temporarily transferred the special task force away for half an hour.

00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:36.060
If the situation changes,

00:07:36.520 --> 00:07:37.780
when you want to leave,

00:07:38.120 --> 00:07:39.280
it won't be so easy.

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:41.640
I won't leave.

00:07:42.080 --> 00:07:43.080
I am needed here.

00:07:44.040 --> 00:07:45.680
From my first day in Harbin,

00:07:46.600 --> 00:07:49.130
I never thought about getting out unscathed.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:58.120
Don't forget you are a girl.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:01.760
If you really fall into the hands of the Japanese,

00:08:01.760 --> 00:08:03.420
you won't be able to handle it.

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:12.360
I will absolutely not let them catch me.

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:16.690
For so many years, I've lived every day

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:18.840
as if it were my last.

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:21.250
Danger is always there.

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:23.140
One careless step,

00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:25.930
and I won't see tomorrow's sun.

00:08:35.640 --> 00:08:36.880
Actually, I think

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.240
you and Lingzi

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:41.280
don't need to live like this.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:42.940
Think about it,

00:08:43.600 --> 00:08:45.460
you can change your way of living.

00:08:47.520 --> 00:08:48.980
With our country in peril,

00:08:49.080 --> 00:08:50.800
we must burn in the dark night.

00:08:52.520 --> 00:08:53.440
Lingzi knows,

00:08:53.840 --> 00:08:55.970
and the telegraph operators know too.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:58.000
What we transmit is not radio waves.

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:00.330
What do you mean?

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:03.770
What we transmit is the appearance of spring.

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:15.400
I like that.

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:17.280
When spring comes,

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:18.640
it won't be so cold.

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:23.280
Alright.

00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:26.780
Lingzi and I will escort you back to the Harmonica Society.

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:36.970
Is this Datong Firm?

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:39.040
Datong Firm.

00:09:39.960 --> 00:09:40.760
Mr. Shen.

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.800
It's me, Qian Yugui.

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.090
Section Chief Qian.

00:09:44.520 --> 00:09:45.400
Don't worry.

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:48.600
President Wang has promised to help you look for it.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:49.360
Take it easy.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:50.880
It will take two or three days.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.680
There will surely be definite news.

00:09:52.680 --> 00:09:54.140
Okay, thank you, Mr. Shen.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.880
I will wait for your news.

00:09:55.880 --> 00:09:56.520
Okay.

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:05.800
Brother, Sister Qin is here.

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:08.720
Brother Shen.

00:10:08.880 --> 00:10:09.680
What's wrong?

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:11.840
Lingzi just got some important intel.

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:13.080
The Japanese Takeuchi Unit

00:10:13.080 --> 00:10:14.140
and the Jingan Army

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:15.360
are going to execute a pincer movement

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:16.800
on the North Manchuria Anti-Japanese United Army.

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:17.840
So tonight,

00:10:18.080 --> 00:10:19.400
I want Cheng Lin and Suying

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:21.080
to send the intel to the United Army

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:22.880
so the troops can relocate in advance.

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:23.920
What time are you transmitting?

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:24.850
Tonight at 9:30.

00:10:25.520 --> 00:10:27.000
Okay, transmit on time.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:28.400
Remember,

00:10:28.560 --> 00:10:29.960
don't transmit it early.

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:31.720
Okay.

00:10:32.120 --> 00:10:33.880
Brother, when dealing with Suzuki Kang,

00:10:33.880 --> 00:10:35.080
you must be careful.

00:10:36.360 --> 00:10:37.160
Don't worry.

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:38.760
At least for tonight,

00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:40.450
he won't be able to find you.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:56.520
Mr. Suzuki,

00:10:56.920 --> 00:10:57.640
look.

00:11:07.960 --> 00:11:08.520
Hurry up!

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.450
Towards the southeast corner.

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:19.840
Let's begin.

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:30.800
Over there,

00:11:31.160 --> 00:11:33.000
that factory with the lights on.

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:34.560
Mr. Suzuki,

00:11:34.800 --> 00:11:36.120
suspicious radio waves detected.

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:37.580
The signal is very strong.

00:11:46.640 --> 00:11:47.400
Chief Qian,

00:11:47.720 --> 00:11:49.080
you and Deputy Chief Chen lead the team

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:50.880
to search over there carefully.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:51.640
Yes.

00:11:53.240 --> 00:11:54.920
Mr. Suzuki, over here.

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:57.520
Leave a team for me.

00:11:58.520 --> 00:11:59.240
Okay.

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:03.760
Squad One, get off.

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:05.720
You follow Officer Suzuki.

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:06.360
Yes, sir.

00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:10.700
Mr. Suzuki,

00:12:10.840 --> 00:12:12.360
maybe Deputy Section Chief Chen and I

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:13.690
should just follow you.

00:12:13.800 --> 00:12:14.920
Section Chief Qian,

00:12:14.920 --> 00:12:15.800
are you questioning

00:12:15.800 --> 00:12:18.080
the soldiers of the Great Japanese Empire?

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:19.010
I wouldn't dare.

00:12:19.640 --> 00:12:20.400
Follow me.

00:12:26.560 --> 00:12:27.890
Get in. We need to hurry.

00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:52.120
This way.

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.480
Another jammer.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:16.920
Bastard.

00:14:01.920 --> 00:14:02.600
Hurry up.

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:18.040
Sent.

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:19.240
Okay, pack up.

00:14:26.400 --> 00:14:27.400
Strange.

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.060
The signal is gone.

00:14:30.640 --> 00:14:31.320
Great.

00:14:31.720 --> 00:14:32.980
All for nothing again.

00:14:33.960 --> 00:14:36.120
I wonder how Mr. Suzuki is doing.

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:31.120
Take him away.